title: Hearts of Iron IV Waking the Tiger-CODEX
description:
E X
P R E S E N T S

Hearts of Iron IV: Waking the Tiger (c) Paradox Interactive

Release Date :  03/2018              Protection : Steam
Discs        :  1                    Genre      : Simulation

Years before Europe went to war, Japans imperial ambitions targeted
the divided Chinese Republic. Crippled by political  paralysis  and
centuries of fitful development, China  is still  not  a  pushover.
With vast reserves of  manpower and  resources, not  to  mention  a
giant landmass, the Republic of China and its temporary  ally,  the
Communists under Mao, can withstand another aggressor.

For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/702350/

- Extract
- Burn or mount the .iso
- Run setup.exe and install
- Copy crack from CODEX dir to installdir
- Play

NOTES: This release is standalone and includes all previously
released content
